import { useState , useEffect} from 'react'; import { Modal , Button, Form} from 'react-bootstrap'; import axios from "axios"; import {Container , Row, Col,FloatingLabel,Dropdown, DropdownButton} from 'react-bootstrap'; import './Profile.css'; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; const Profile = () => { const [name,setName] = useState("Someone") const [role,setRole] = useState("actor") useEffect( async () =>{ try { await axios.get("https://localhost:44323/api/GetProfileInfo") .then((responce) => { setRole(responce.data['role']) setName(responce.data['firstName']) }) } catch (error) { console.error(error) } console.log(role) }) return(

{name}

{role}

Update Personal Details

First Name Last Name New Phone Number

Update Account Details

New Email address New Password
); } export default Profile;
